creator: Inspectly
descriptionHtml:
This is our new app from 2022!

Inspectly offers IT solutions for digitalising and optimising your quality management, and for granting you insight into making your work processes more effective and efficient. From easy and intuitive on-site mobile documentation to a complete overview from the administration system, Inspectly supports your day-to-day tasks and quality management.

Inspectly’s modules and IT solutions are tailored to contractors working within the construction industry:

- Quality Assurance and Control
- Change Orders for Contractors
- Photo Documentation
- Punch Lists
- Checklists
- Inspection and Safety Walks
- Task Management
- Document Storage

With full support and onboarding from the Inspectly Team, templates such as industry standard checklists, and various possible integrations to utilise, Inspectly is fully flexible to perfectly suit your specific needs.

Anywhere, anytime
Inspectly is designed to make the distance between construction site and office as short as possible. On-site workers can register on mobile devices both online and offline, and registration and journalising are completed in one action. With immediate access to the documentation, project managers can follow progress remotely and in real-time for a complete overview. Additionally, registrations can be made and accessed as general lists or as marks on floorplans.

Everything on one platform
All registrations and documentation are automatically journalised in Inspectly. With one central platform for documentation, journalising, and reporting, you can easily store, export, and compile your information into orderly reports.

Gain value in the long term
Inspectly gives you a transparent overview, and you will thus gain insight into your processes and identify areas that can be optimised. Being fully aware lets you improve your work processes to avoid defects, disputes, and economic loss in the future.

This is our new app from 2022!

Inspectly offers IT solutions for digitalising and optimising your quality management, and for granting you insight into making your work processes more effective and efficient. From easy and intuitive on-site mobile documentation to a complete overview from the administration system, Inspectly supports your day-to-day tasks and quality management.

Inspectly’s modules and IT solutions are tailored to contractors working within the construction industry:

- Quality Assurance and Control
- Change Orders for Contractors
- Photo Documentation
- Punch Lists
- Checklists
- Inspection and Safety Walks
- Task Management
- Document Storage

With full support and onboarding from the Inspectly Team, templates such as industry standard checklists, and various possible integrations to utilise, Inspectly is fully flexible to perfectly suit your specific needs.

Anywhere, anytime
Inspectly is designed to make the distance between construction site and office as short as possible. On-site workers can register on mobile devices both online and offline, and registration and journalising are completed in one action. With immediate access to the documentation, project managers can follow progress remotely and in real-time for a complete overview. Additionally, registrations can be made and accessed as general lists or as marks on floorplans.

Everything on one platform
All registrations and documentation are automatically journalised in Inspectly. With one central platform for documentation, journalising, and reporting, you can easily store, export, and compile your information into orderly reports.

Gain value in the long term
Inspectly gives you a transparent overview, and you will thus gain insight into your processes and identify areas that can be optimised. Being fully aware lets you improve your work processes to avoid defects, disputes, and economic loss in the future.

title:
Inspectly App
6.2.58

creator: Inspectly
descriptionHtml:
This is our new app from 2022!

Inspectly offers IT solutions for digitalising and optimising your quality management, and for granting you insight into making your work processes more effective and efficient. From easy and intuitive on-site mobile documentation to a complete overview from the administration system, Inspectly supports your day-to-day tasks and quality management.

Inspectly’s modules and IT solutions are tailored to contractors working within the construction industry:

- Quality Assurance and Control
- Change Orders for Contractors
- Photo Documentation
- Punch Lists
- Checklists
- Inspection and Safety Walks
- Task Management
- Document Storage

With full support and onboarding from the Inspectly Team, templates such as industry standard checklists, and various possible integrations to utilise, Inspectly is fully flexible to perfectly suit your specific needs.

Anywhere, anytime
Inspectly is designed to make the distance between construction site and office as short as possible. On-site workers can register on mobile devices both online and offline, and registration and journalising are completed in one action. With immediate access to the documentation, project managers can follow progress remotely and in real-time for a complete overview. Additionally, registrations can be made and accessed as general lists or as marks on floorplans.

Everything on one platform
All registrations and documentation are automatically journalised in Inspectly. With one central platform for documentation, journalising, and reporting, you can easily store, export, and compile your information into orderly reports.

Gain value in the long term
Inspectly gives you a transparent overview, and you will thus gain insight into your processes and identify areas that can be optimised. Being fully aware lets you improve your work processes to avoid defects, disputes, and economic loss in the future.
